data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS AND A HOME WARRANTY!  Introducing this expansive 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence nestled in the sought-after Northgate at Legacy Park community. Its open floor plan offers a seamless flow to the family room, a spacious kitchen with a breakfast bar, and a separate dining room. This home features generously sized bedrooms, and the master bedroom boasts trey ceilings, his and hers closets, and a private bath with a garden tub and a separate shower. Recent enhancements feature beautiful LVP flooring gracing the entire main level, newly installed windows with the added benefit of a warranty, and a fresh backyard fence for your comfort and security. Enjoy amenities such as pool and tennis. Minutes from Hwy 75, Downtown Acworth/Kennesaw, shops, restaurants, top West Cobb schools, and award-winning parks.
